title: GET_VEHICLE_FLIGHT_NOZZLE_POSITION
content:
0xAD40AD55// GetVehicleFlightNozzlePosition
float GET_VEHICLE_FLIGHT_NOZZLE_POSITION(Vehicle vehicle);Parameters:vehicle: The vehicle to check.Returns: The flight nozzel position between 0.0 (flying normally) and 1.0 (VTOL mode)Gets the flight nozzel position for the specified vehicle. See the client-side _GET_VEHICLE_FLIGHT_NOZZLE_POSITION native for usage examples.
codeBlocks:
local ped = PlayerPedId()
local vehicle = GetVehiclePedIsIn(ped, false)
-- Example usage for GET_VEHICLE_FLIGHT_NOZZLE_POSITION
GetVehicleFlightNozzlePosition(vehicle)
